
# Installation

The easiest way to install is via opam:

    opam init
    opam remote add xen-org git://github.com/xen-org/opam-repo-dev
    opam install xcp-rrdd

# Coverage Profiling

This code can be instrumented for coverage profiling. See
[COVERAGE.md](./COVERAGE.md) for details and [profiling/](./profiling/)
for supporting code.

    make coverage
    make


